emake Of James Corden\u2019s BAFTA-Winning \u2018A League Of Their Own\u2019|last=Kanter|first=Jake|last2=Kanter|first2=Jake|date=2019-11-06|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2020-02-11}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Title\n!Artist\n!Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2017\n|\"[[Swish Swish]]\"\n|[[Katy Perry]] feat. [[Nicki Minaj]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.masslive.com/patriots/2017/08/new_england_patriots_te_rob_gr_11.html |title=New England Patriots TE Rob Gronkowski makes cameo in bizarre Katy Perry music video |last=O'Malley |first=Nick |date=2017-08-24 |website=MassLive |language=en |access-date=2019-09-30}}</ref>\n|-\n|\"On My Mind\"\n|[[3LAU]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bostonmagazine.com/arts-entertainment/2017/05/25/rob-gronkowski-3lau-music-video/ |title=Rob Gronkowski Starred in a Music Video |last=Sullivan |first=Eliza |date=2017-05-25 |website=Boston Magazine |language=en-US |access-date=2019-09-30}}</ref>\n|-\n|2020\n|\"I'll Wait\"\n|[[Kygo]]\n|with [[Camille Kostek]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oSPvNybEYxQ|title=KYGO - I'll Wait (Rob Gronkowski & Camille Kostek)|last=|first=|date=|website=YouTube|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Gronkowski (horse)]], a racehorse named after, and partly owned by, Rob Gronkowski<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.si.com/nfl/2018/06/05/rob-gronkowski-horse-belmont-stakes |title=Despite underdog status, Rob Gronkowski is all in on his horse |last=Kahler |first=Kalyn |date=June 5, 2018 |website=SI.com |language=en |access-date=2019-09-30}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n* {{Footballstats |nfl=497240 |espn=13229 |pfr=G/GronRo00}}\n* [https://arizonawildcats.com/roster.aspx?rp_id=147 Arizona Wildcats profile]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20161109062933/http://www.patriots.com/team/players/roster/rob-gronkowski New England Patriots biography]\n