 Talents Of The Kids From \"Stranger Things\"|website=[[BuzzFeed]]|date=August 2, 2016|accessdate=September 19, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.playbill.com/person/caleb-mclaughlin-vault-0000123644|title=Caleb McLaughlin|website=[[Playbill]]|accessdate=September 19, 2016}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Nominated work\n! Result\n! {{Abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n| [[38th Young Artist Awards|2017]]\n| [[38th Young Artist Awards|Young Artist Awards]]\n| [[38th Young Artist Awards#Best Performance in a Digital TV Series or Film|Best Performance in a Digital TV Series or Film&nbsp;\u2013 Teen Actor]] \n| rowspan=\"8\"| ''[[Stranger Things (TV series)|Stranger Things]]'' \n| {{nom}}\n| <ref name=\"2016YAA\">{{cite web|title=38th Annual Awards |url=http://www.youngartistawards.org/noms25.htm |publisher=[[Young Artist Association]] |accessdate=January 7, 2018 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202050908/http://youngartistawards.org/nominees |archivedate=January 7, 2018 }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[23rd Screen Actors Guild Awards|2017]]\n| [[Screen Actors Guild Award]]s\n| [[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by an Ensemble in a Drama Series|Outstanding Performance by an Ensemble in a Drama Series]]  \n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ew.com/article/2016/12/14/2017-sag-awards-nominations|title=SAG Awards nominations 2017: See the full list|website=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|first=Joely|last=Nolfi|date=14 December 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[BET Awards 2017|2017]]\n| [[BET Awards]]\n| [[BET Awards 2017|YoungStars Award]]\n| {{Nom}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bet.com/shows/bet-awards/2017/nominees/youngstars-award.html |title=Youngstars Award |website=[[BET Awards 2017]] |date=June 25, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[49th NAACP Image Awards|2018]]\n| [[NAACP Image Awards]]\n| [[NAACP Image Award for Outstanding Performance by a Youth (Series, Special, Television M